backend.queue
Class InstructorQueue

java.lang.Object
  backend.queue.InstructorQueue

public class InstructorQueue
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains all the ProgramQueues associated with an instructor. A ProgramQueue should exists for every program that exists, unless the file heirarchy has been changed since the last login.

Author:
Kayre Hylton
